metadata.name: ROADMAP OG 100
metadata.description:
My name is Dariush Raad, I`m a Web 3.0 creator and an adventurer, so I kinda have to do this! I`m going to walk and hitchhike 3000 km and write the journey on the blockchain daily. This is OG 100, The Genesis of the "ROADMAP" project. Also The First Draft I`ve ever designed around this Idea.

It is an ERC1155 token to support this Journey and a way to track and remember good souls who have been walking beside me on the road.


This Token is originally listed for 0.03 ETH in 100 Editions. 
(To match it with 3000 km for the mathematic game, LFG)
